  → development/OpenStreetMap/API/Overpass/js/osmtogeojson[Using osmtogeojson] to convert an → development/OpenStreetMap/API/Overpass result into → development/languages/JavaScript/JSON/GeoJSON.

  → development/web/HTML/tags/input/type/button/onclick[`onclick` handler] of HTML buttons.
